The paper deals with testing properties of multivariate functions over finite fields, which is a topic that falls under computational complexity (cs.CC). The use of Fourier analysis suggests that the paper may also belong to information theory (cs.IT) or data structures (cs.DS). The development of graph-theoretic techniques in an algebraic setting may also place the paper in the categories of discrete mathematics (cs.DM) or computational geometry (cs.CG).
